Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:14.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:22.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:26.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:34.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:44.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:03.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:15.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:18.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:24.71,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,200.389)}The Monstrous Namekujira's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:24.71,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,690.389)}Gas Explosion Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the computer brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks so small!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the smallest computer\Nbrain in history, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Yajima,\Njust what is it capable of?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider my computer brain\Nto be a miniature computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've implanted the computer brain\Ninto the head of this rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It can then make the rabbit capable\Nof understanding all human speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A rabbit? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Seems unbelievable!\N- Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer brain's\Nother function
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is the ability to maximize an\Nanimal's special attributes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, before this,\Nthis rabbit was capable
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of jumping approximately\None meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer brain, though,\Nallows it to jump five meters with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Five meters?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's have an\Nexperiment, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a big jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of what would happen\Nif you put that into a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Shocker's\Ngonna want that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To defeat the Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,who stands in the way of Shocker's\Nplans for world domination,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I must create even more powerful\Ncyborgs than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To accomplish this,\Nyou must steal Doctor Yajima's invention,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the computer brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Namekujira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. A computer brain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A man could make a lot of money\Nwith something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.41,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\3c&H34303A&\c&H000000&}Yajima
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ready?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A little higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the computer brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right below us,\Njust as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for the guided vacuum tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Close it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just an illusion!\NLet's get out of here, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer brain is protected\Nby an infrared sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,An alarm will go off the\Nsecond anyone touches it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean,\Nsomeone was in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... there's no sign\Nof anyone entering, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Bro. Let's call it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can get\Nthrough security that tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna steal that computer brain\Nand sell it off to another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll fetch 300 million\Nyen, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You think this thing's\Nworth 300 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just grab it and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five,\Nsix, seven, eight, nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirteen, fourteen,\Nfifteen, sixteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that artificial brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we're giving it up after\Nwe worked that hard to steal it! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to die, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He says we'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better run quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown yourself,\NShocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I implanted you with\Nthat computer brain, Namekujira,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I could increase the power of your\Nliquid jets dozens of times over,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing you to even melt\Nthrough these steel gasholders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that Kamen Rider has\Narrived, our plans have changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry!\NI'll get some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I always take care of girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:12.79,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes and look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, listen closely to\Nwhat I am about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When the clock strikes ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,feed this tranquilizer\Nto Ichimonji and Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all worried about\Nyou, Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not gonna have\Nsome, Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, since I'm going to bed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be exhausted from\Nall that worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm suddenly very sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\NI think I'll get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, please continue\Nto handle security.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good night.\N- Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A special FBI antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably just\Na tranquilizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll recover on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... time to see what they\Nhave planned for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer brain is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We should watch and see how\Nthey're controlling Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NThey'll slip up sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NIs the surgery still in progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:16:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't figure out how to\Nconnect the computer brain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to his nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we can\Nperform the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. I've already\Ntaken the appropriate measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I know how to use\Nthe computer brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would take it?\NAnd to what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working now, dear.\NPlease leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Yajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be\Nstartled, Doctor Yajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter is currently\Nunder Shocker's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want her to\Ndie, follow her to our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the one who stole\Nthe computer brain was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Your very own daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How far must I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn right at the next light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting a signal\Nfrom Taki's transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put a stop to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Namekujira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power should be\Namplified by dozens of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate our gasholder\Ndetonation plan at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gasholder detonation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to use my\Ncomputer brain for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Yajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me give you a demonstration\Nof Namekujira's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to the next plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The next plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They said something about\Nblowing up gasholders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance... blow it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for\Nyou, Namekujira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you touch\Nthese holding tanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here, Namekujira!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Double Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:23:01.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rider's heroics kept Tokyo\Nfrom a gas detonation disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:04.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker's evil\Nwould not be dissuaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:10.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rider renews his pledge to fight\Nwhatever enemies tomorrow brings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:10.51,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:13.95,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:14.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:16.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the snowy mountain\Nmonster Bearkonger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:19.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Exciting action unfolds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:22.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,as Rider skids through the\NKusatsu Highlands on a snowmobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:24.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:28.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Showdown!!\NSnowy Mountain Monster Bearkonger!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:30.65,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy80\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,215.389)}Showdown!! Snowy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:30.65,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs130\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,690.389)}Mountain Monster Bearkonger
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:40.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:43.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:45.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:48.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:50.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:54.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:55.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:58.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:03.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:07.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.33,0:24:10.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:15.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Namekujira's\NGas Explosion Plan